<SECOND>PM-Sniper,0533</SECOND>
<HEAD>Landlady Unaware She Rented Room to Self-Styled Commando</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By PAT MILTON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>RIVERHEAD, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
