oings. <PERSON> Chun </PERSON>, 58, left office last February. He has denied any personal corruption, but surrendered $ 24 million in illegal political funds before going into rural exile. Radical students and dissidents have demonstrated frequently in recent months, demanding <PERSON> Chun </PERSON> be punished for alleged corruption and human rights violations.
